hopobject.body: What do you like doing in your spare time? isotretinoin cancer treatment The new My Cloud OS and system architecture allows more dynamic response to queries from mobile apps, including delivering thumbnails for photos and music artwork, WD said. The mobile apps are also "smarter" about delivering content. For example, on the new WD Photos app, if you download 30,000 files onto the My Cloud, it will now tell a user that it is processing the files. "Our My Cloud app will also display this content (including thumbnails)," WD stated.
